HEADWORD: Ecclesia
<hw>Ec*cle"si*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Ecclesi⟦ae⟧</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L., fr. Gr.
